- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses computable winning strategies, which is a common topic in AI research. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the synthesis of correct control and monitoring code for cyber-physical systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the synthesis of code for safety-critical systems. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is less likely but still possible as the paper introduces a new logic with soundness and consistency proofs.
